he support of his two sons. The Prophet said, \u201cWhat is the matter with this man?\u201d They said, \u201cHe has vowed to walk to the Ka\u2019bah.\u201d The Prophet said, \u201cAllah does not need this\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":15610,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/08\/07\/ramadan-umrah-hajj\/","url_meta":{"origin":40735,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Pilgrimage: &#8216;Umrah in Ramadan equal to Hajj","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"August 7, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Ibn Abbas reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \"Verily, the 'Umrah pilgrimage during Ramadan is equal to Hajj.\" Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 1782, S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Muslim 1256 Grade: Muttafaqun Alayhi\u00a0(authenticity agreed upon) according to Al-Bukhari and Muslim \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0627\u0628\u0652\u0646\u0650 \u0639\u064e\u0628\u0651\u064e\u0627\u0633\u064d \u0623\u064e\u0646\u0651\u064e \u0627\u0644\u0646\u0651\u064e\u0628\u0650\u064a\u0651\u064e \u0635\u064e\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0649 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0647\u064f \u0639\u064e\u0644\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0647\u0650 \u0648\u064e\u0633\u064e\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0645\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0625\u0650\u0646\u0651\u064e\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":37056,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2021\/09\/28\/mushrikun